text: Hinnak Nabii Mucammad Jcsakeýķe marak koroosite mari Mucammad ġa ama Qhuraan ginnaasiteh iyyaa? Nabiyow anu ama Qhuraan diraabah ginnaasite yoo tekkek, toysa yi dambi yol yaniih, anu nummat yaaba num ekkek, toysa umeynit siiniiy anu sin koroosannuu kee isin abtan umaanek bari kinniyo keenik ixxic
